The paper deals with the construction of quantum codes, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). It also involves the study of error-correcting codes (cs.ET) and cryptography (cs.CR), as well as the use of algebraic structures (cs.DS) and mathematical optimization (cs.SD) in the construction of these codes.
